title: Logano spins out Kenseth late, wins at Kansas Speedway
text:
> North Carolina Logano spins out Kenseth late, wins at Kansas Speedway Sprint Cup Series driver Joey Logano burns out after winning a NASCAR auto race at Kansas Speedway in Kansas City, Kan., Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015.
